Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.87,1:22:20.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想来 也许从一开始那座岛就注定会变成这样
Dialogue: 0,1:22:24.12,1:22:25.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永别了
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.27,1:22:27.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.12,1:22:36.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 我们走吧
